------------------------------------------------------------<br>
Chardok Nobles, Plane of Hate, Plane of Fear can not be booked 2 days in a row.<br>
Nagafen, Vox can not be booked 2 spawns in a row.<br>
Plane of Air can be booked for multiple continous days due to the nature of the zone.<br>
<br>
No reservation can be made more than 2 weeks in advance.  The technical exception is PoA, provided the first day of the raid is not booked more than 2 weeks in advance.<br>
<br>
Boss mobs in PoF/PoH: making a reservation does NOT automatically entitle you to boss mobs.  The only restriction to taking out boss mobs before a scheduled raid is you must allow sufficient time after your boss mob kill for a full respawn of the plane before the scheduled start time of the next raid. (If there is a Hate raid planned for noon on Friday, feel free to drop in unreserved and wax Inny on Thursday night, just be gone before midnight.  Provided it's a 12 hour respawn, I forget.)<br>
<br>
Special Nagafen/Vox spawns: in the event of unscheduled server downtime, the spawn is FFA provided it does not cause the disruption of a previously scheduled raid.  (Server crashes on Monday, spawning Naggy.  Raid scheduled for Wednesday, when he should have spawned.  Naggy is hands off so he's still up for Wednesday's raid.)  For scheduled server downtime, if Nagafen/Vox are up and there are no scheduled raids prior to the scheduled outage, they are FFA targets of opportunity.  (Raid wipes on Vox on Sunday.  Server is scheduled for downtime on Tuesday.  Vox is now FFA.)<br>
<br>
If you're going to roll on Hate or Fear for boss mobs when there is no reservation, take 5 minutes and post a quick reservation.  That way when someone sees you're there, drops out and tries to make a quick reservation to say you ganked them, you're covered. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
The calendar day starts and ends at midnight Eastern.<br>
------------------------------------------------------------<br>
OK, maybe not so simple, but this covers some issues that, historically, have been major points of contention and had no rules to fall back on concerning them, namely boss mobs and server outage spawns.<br>
<br>
Incidently, I also have scheduled my share of raids, and don't ever recall a 2 week between reservations rule.<br>
<br>
